    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54 platform, featuring the legendary 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is absolute; the rod bearings and subframe\u2014critical points for this chassis\u2014have been proactively addressed and reinforced. Power is transmitted through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring linear torque delivery. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. With a pristine undercarriage and no signs of thermal cycling fatigue on the headers, this is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
